        },
        {
            "label": "Configurar PYTHONPATH",
            "type": "shell",
            "command": "echo $(pwd) > .venv/lib/python3.12/site-packages/main.pth" // ? - Para evitar problemas com o PYTHONPATH e ter que adicionar o diret贸rio do projeto manualmente, veja mais em https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10738919/how-do-i-add-a-path-to-pythonpath-in-virtualenv#:~:text=Add%20a%20comment-,7%20Answers,-Sorted%20by%3A
        },
        {
            "label": "Adicionar arquivo credentials.py",
            "type": "shell",
            "command": "echo ''> app/Config/credentials.py"
        },
        {
            "label": "Criar pastas adicionais",
            "type": "shell",
            "command": "mkdir app/assets; mkdir app/data"
        },
        // TEST Tasks
        {
            "label": "pylint",
            "type": "shell",
            "command": "pylint $(dir 'app' -r | % { if ($_.PsIsContainer) { } else { $_.FullName } }) --ignore-paths=^.*\\__pycache__\\.*$,^.*.ipynb$"
        },
        // PROD Tasks
        {
            "label": "Formatar c贸digo",
